and control in whole or in part as hereinafter provided, will be under the charge and control of the Bidder and during
such period of control by the Bidder all risks in connection therewith and the materials to be used therein will be borne
by the Bidder. The Bidder will make good and fully repair all injuries and damages to the Project or any portion thereof
under the control of the Bidder, by reason of any act of God or other casualty or cause, whether or not the same shall have
occurred by reason of the Bidder's negligence. 
